dead within 30 feet of yourself. You also sense whether the Hallow spell is active there and, if so, where.\n\nThe spell is blocked by 1 foot of stone, dirt, or wood; 1 inch of metal; or a thin sheet of lead"}, "classes": {"value": ["cleric", "paladin"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.608822"}, "id": "detect_evil_and_good"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Detect Magic"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_1"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_divination"}, "ritual": {"value": true}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "Self (30-foot radius)"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 10 minutes"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "description": {"value": "For the duration, you sense the presence of magical effects within 30 feet of yourself. If you sense such effects, you can take the Magic action to see a faint aura around any visible creature or object in the area that bears the magic, and if an effect was created by a spell, you learn the spell's school of magic.\n\nThe spell is blocked by 1 foot of stone, dirt, or wood; 1 inch of metal; or a thin sheet of lead"}, "classes": {"value": ["bard", "cleric", "druid", "paladin", "ranger", "sorcerer", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard", "warlock"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.608985"}, "id": "detect_magic"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Clairvoyance"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_3"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_divination"}, "casting_time": {"value": "10 minutes"}, "range": {"value": "1 mile"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 10 minutes"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a focus worth at least 100gp, either a jeweled horn for hearing or a glass eye for seeing"}, 